channel.title: Help - possible?
channel.description:
[b][i]Hi I've been a member to MoparScape for a long time (well I forgot my last accounts password :mad:) but I've never seen this once in my life of being registered/browsing as a guest...[/i][/b]
[i]Now I'd like to know if this is possible and how to do it - You don't have to post with help, but you can atleast post with information if it's possible.[/i]
Ok now down to the help part: [b][i]Is it possible to add walls like the Edgeville Bank walls, is it possible to add them into another place on my map? Not like the object walls, the ACTUAL walls that you can't right click and get the ID[/i][/b]
